org_pef_text.pef2text
Interface AbstractEmbosser

All Known Implementing Classes:
BrailleFileExporter, ConfigurableEmbosser
public interface AbstractEmbosser

PEF oriented embosser interface. Note! Interface is a draft. Contact author before implementing an embosser based on this interface

Since:
1.0
Version:
10 okt 2008
Author:
Joel Hakansson, TPB
